        <h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p class="">
            I like to create things that are both functional and easy to use. On the web that means focussing on both
            form and function, never forgetting that the user is the most important part of the equation. Every day I
            strive to become a little bit better at what I do.
          </p>
          <!-- <p class="pt-2"></p> -->
          <!-- <p>
          </p> -->
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="animate-fade">
        <h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
